# Awesome Project Build with Apollo GraphQL + Typescript + TypeORM

Steps to run this project:

1. Run `yarn` command
2. Run `yarn typeorm:fixtures` command
3. Run `yarn start` command

# Apollo Server GraphQL

## Queries:
```gql
query GET_CATEGORIES {
  categories {
    id
    name
  }
}

query GET_ALL_BOOK($page: Int = 1, $perPage: Int = 15, $filter: BookFilter) {
  getAllBook(page: $page, perPage: $perPage, filter: $filter) {
    total
    hasMore
    items {
      ...Product
      ...Book
    }
  }
}

query GET_BOOK($slug: String!) {
  book(slug: $slug) {
    ...Product
    ...Book
  }
}

fragment Book on Book {
  publisher
  isbn
  edition
  language
  country
  numberOfPage
  author {
    id
    name
    bio
  }
}

fragment Product on Product {
  id
  slug
  title
  description
  price
  salePrice
  discountInPtion NEW_NOTIFICATION {
  newNotification {
		message
    date
	}
}ercent
  categories {

}
```

## Mutations:
```gql
mutation ADD_BOOK($input: BookInput!) {
	saveBook(input: $input) {
    ...Product
   	...Book
  }
}

mutation UPDATE_BOOK($id: ID!, $input: BookInput!) {
	saveBook(id: $id, input: $input) {
    ...Product
   	...Book
  }
}

mutation DELETE_BOOK($id: ID!) {
	deleted: deleteBook(id: $id)
}

fragment Book on Book {
  publisher
  isbn
  edition
  language
  country
  numberOfPage
}

fragment Product on Product {
  id
  slug
  title
  description
  price
  salePrice
  discountInPercent
  categories {
    id
    name
  }
}
```
